or what this is about?

91
00:04:46.542 --> 00:04:47.458
No.

92
00:04:48.458 --> 00:04:50.417
[police siren wailing faintly]

93
00:04:51.625 --> 00:04:53.417
I'm sorry. Soâ€¦

94
00:04:54.417 --> 00:04:57.333
