-Like what?

161
00:08:25.583 --> 00:08:26.917
Believe him. for starters.

162
00:08:30.625 --> 00:08:32.667
I need to see my boy again. Philip.

163
00:08:38.250 --> 00:08:39.667
[Adam] Appreciate your help.

164
00:08:41.833 --> 00:08:45.042
You're not gonna believe this.
My friend checked the DOT database.

165
00:08:45.125 --> 00:08:48.167
The reason there's
no accident report in the file

166
