No. not possible.

168
00:08:52.292 --> 00:08:54.167
Detectives would've
verified Cheryl's story.

169
00:08:54.250 --> 00:08:55.542
They did.

170
00:08:56.667 --> 00:09:00.958
The detectives spoke to aâ€¦
a hospital administrator. Yeah. here.

171
00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:03.583
He confirmed

172
00:09:04.208 --> 00:09:08.167
Cheryl was called into the hospital
that night due to a bus accident.

173
00:09:09.417 --> 00:09:10.667
[Philip] Ronald Dreason.

174
