198
00:10:28.542 --> 00:10:29.667
[Cheryl] Thank you.

199
00:10:30.875 --> 00:10:31.917
Boy or girl?

200
00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:34.000
It's a girl.

201
00:10:38.958 --> 00:10:39.958
