207
00:10:58.917 --> 00:11:01.125
I think I know
why David broke out of prison.

208
00:11:01.750 --> 00:11:03.542
Yeah. me too.

209
00:11:04.042 --> 00:11:04.875
Rachel called.

210
00:11:08.292 --> 00:11:09.958
Matthew's gone. Lenny.

211
00:11:12.042 --> 00:11:14.167
Nothing we can do will change that.

212
00:11:15.292 --> 00:11:17.375
Yeah. you're probably right. But. uhâ€¦

213
