The hospital administrator.

222
00:11:45.500 --> 00:11:47.917
-Ronald?
-Yes. Ronald.

223
00:11:48.625 --> 00:11:49.625
What does it matter?

224
00:11:49.708 --> 00:11:54.000
It matters because there were
no bus accidents that night. Cheryl.

225
00:11:54.958 --> 00:11:56.917
-Of course there was.
-No.

226
00:11:57.583 --> 00:11:58.667
According to the MTA.

227
00:11:58.750 --> 00:12:02.292
