in the Greater Boston Area that night.

228
00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:05.833
That. umâ€¦ That doesn't make any sense.

229
00:12:06.625 --> 00:12:10.167
I agree. That's why I want
to talk to Ronald about it.

230
00:12:11.625 --> 00:12:13.667
