233
00:12:23.250 --> 00:12:24.250
Yeah.

234
00:12:25.375 --> 00:12:26.375
You're right.

235
00:12:27.625 --> 00:12:29.000
I shouldn't have come.

236
00:12:31.583 --> 00:12:32.667
It was good to see you.

237
00:12:39.417 --> 00:12:40.625
I'm happy for you.

238
00:12:42.375 --> 00:12:43.375
I really am.

239
00:12:50.333 --> 00:12:52.458
[phone line ringing]

240
00:13:00.125 --> 00:13:02.625
[Dreason's voice]You've reached
Ronald Dreason of Boston General.

241
00:13:02.708 --> 00:13:03.750
Leave a message.

242
00:13:03.833 --> 00:13:07.375
I need to talk to you. Will you call me
back as soon as you get this?

243
00:13:07.458 --> 00:13:09.375
[dramatic music playing]

244
00:13:13.833 --> 00:13:15.542
[David] You never struck me as a gun guy.

245
00:13:16.125 --> 00:13:18.125
My mother's a bit of a worrier.

246
00:13:18.208 --> 00:13:20.917
Always felt better knowing
that I had a gun in the apartment.

247
00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:23.292
